User Guide

Programmable Liquidity for Solana Tokens

Version 1.0 | December 2025

Getting Started

Welcome to PumpLogic! This guide will walk you through setting up and using all features of the platform.

What is PumpLogic?

PumpLogic is a DeFi platform that enables Solana token creators to automatically route fees into:

  • Market Making - Improve trading depth and volume
  • Buyback - Support token price with strategic purchases
  • Liquidity Pool - Build deeper DEX liquidity
  • Creator Revenue - Your earnings as the creator

Connect Your Wallet

1 Visit pumplogic.live
2 Click "Connect Wallet" in the top right
3 Approve the Phantom wallet connection
4 You're in! Your dashboard is now live.

Dashboard Overview

The dashboard is your command center for managing fee distributions. Once you connect your wallet, you'll see:

Allocation Sliders

Set percentages for each distribution category

Quick Actions

Access wallets, alerts, token settings, and presets

Manual Distribution

Send fees to configured wallets with one click

Activity Log

Track all transactions with Solscan links

Setting Up Fee Allocations

Configure how your fees are distributed across the four categories.

1 Use the sliders to set each category's percentage
2 Ensure the total adds up to 100%
3 Click "Save Allocations" to confirm
Pro Tip

Use the "Save Preset" button to save your favorite configurations for quick access later!

Configuring Destination Wallets

Set up where your fees should be sent for each category.

1 Click "Wallets" in the dashboard
2 Enter a Solana wallet address for each category
3 Click "Save Wallets" to confirm
Best Practice

Use separate wallets for each category for easier tracking. Your revenue wallet can be your personal wallet!

Manual Distribution

Distribute accumulated fees to your configured wallets.

1 Enter the SOL amount in "Manual Distribution"
2 Click "Preview" to see the breakdown
3 Review where each portion goes
4 Click "Distribute Now" and sign in Phantom

Your fees are split and sent to all destination wallets in one transaction!

Using the AI Optimizer

Let AI analyze market conditions and suggest optimal allocations.

1 Find "Smart Optimizer" on your dashboard
2 Click "Run AI"
3 Wait for the analysis (checks network TPS, volatility, etc.)
4 Review the suggested allocations
5 Apply with one click!

Setting Up Telegram Alerts

Get real-time notifications for whale purchases and fee accumulation.

Connect Telegram

1 Open Telegram and find @PumpLogicBot
2 Send /start to get your Chat ID
3 Click "Alerts" on your dashboard
4 Paste your Chat ID and choose notification types

What You'll Get Notified About

  • Whale Alerts - Large purchases (10,000+ tokens)
  • Fee Ready Alerts - When your fee wallet crosses 0.01 SOL
  • Distribution Confirmations - Full breakdown with Solscan links

Token Settings & Monitoring

Configure your token details for blockchain monitoring.

1 Click "Token" in your dashboard
2 Enter your token's contract address (CA)
3 Add your token name and symbol
4 Save - monitoring starts automatically!
How It Works

PumpLogic monitors the Solana blockchain for YOUR token's activity every 30 seconds. Combined with Telegram alerts, you'll know instantly when big moves happen!

Activity Log & Export

Track all your distribution history with full transparency.

View Transaction Details

  • Transaction type (Distribution, Optimize, etc.)
  • Amounts and details
  • Solscan links for on-chain verification
  • Timestamps for all activities

Export Your Data

Click "Export CSV" to download your complete transaction history. Perfect for:

  • Record keeping
  • Tax documentation
  • Showing your community you're legit!

Quick Presets

Switch between different allocation strategies with one click.

Built-in Presets

Aggressive Buyback

Maximum buying pressure to support token price

Liquidity Focus

Build deep pools for better trading

Balanced

Even distribution across all categories

Creator Max

Maximize your revenue earnings

Save Custom Presets

1 Set your preferred allocations
2 Click "Save Preset"
3 Name your preset
4 Load it anytime with one click!

You're Ready!

You now have everything you need to use PumpLogic effectively.

Quick Tips for Success

  • Use a dedicated fee wallet for cleaner tracking
  • Set up Telegram alerts BEFORE your token launches
  • Save your favorite allocation presets
  • Check the AI optimizer for market-aware suggestions
  • Export your CSV regularly for records
